            "body": "does anyone know of other servers that implement this besides copilot-language-server ?\n\n@ofseed besides https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/4029 , what are the steps for a user to try this out?\n\n1. install copilot\n   ```\n   npm install --global @github/copilot-language-server\n   ```\n3. update to Nvim 0.12 (latest master)\n4. `vim.lsp.enable('copilot')`\n5. `:LspCopilotSignIn`\n6. Enable inline completion by `vim.lsp.inline_completion.enable()`\n7. Set keymap for `vim.lsp.inline_completion.get()` and invoke the keymap.",
